<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">风传花信，雨濯春尘第116个“三八”国际妇女节携百年历史的分量与春日一同抵达让我们致敬每一个闪闪发光的「她」</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>国际妇女节的由来</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">国际劳动妇女节（International Working Women's Day），又称三八妇女节，定于每年3月8日。它源于20世纪初全球妇女争取平等、权益与和平的抗争，是为致敬女性在经济、政治、社会各领域的卓越贡献而设立的国际性节日。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>三月春风，暖意渐浓--致敬每一个她</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">三月春风暖，巾帼绽芳华。在第116个国际劳动妇女节到来之际，经济管理学院开展妇女节簪花主题活动，为学院全体女师生送上温馨的节日祝福，以一场雅致美好的仪式，致敬每一位闪闪发光的她。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578467744.jpg" alt="1773578467744.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578467744.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578496840.jpg" alt="1773578496840.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578496840.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>簪花赴春约，共庆妇女节</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578523722.jpg" alt="1773578523722.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578523722.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578536762.jpg" alt="1773578536762.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578536762.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">活动现场温馨美好、暖意融融。大家围坐一起，巧手簪花，将朵朵鲜花轻簪于发间。一簪一饰，尽显温婉优雅；一颦一笑，皆是自信光芒。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578558882.jpg" alt="1773578558882.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578558882.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578572095.jpg" alt="1773578572095.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578572095.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在指尖与繁花的相遇中，大家沉浸式感受传统美学的韵味，在轻松美好的氛围里卸下疲惫、共度温馨时光，展现出朝气蓬勃、温婉大方的最美风采。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>愿所有美好，皆属于“她”</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578595578.jpg" alt="1773578595578.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578595578.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578615458.jpg" alt="1773578615458.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578615458.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578635342.jpg" alt="1773578635342.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578635342.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578656444.jpg" alt="1773578656444.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578656444.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578668022.jpg" alt="1773578668022.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773578668022.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">致每一个闪闪发光的她：愿你不被岁月抹去光芒，不被定义束缚模样，心中有热爱，眼里有光芒，手中有力量，生活有温柔。愿你永远自在如风，自信坦荡，芳华永驻。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">祝所有了不起的她，妇女节快乐！</span></p>